-- CANADA RESEARCH ROUNDUP-Avigilon, CI Financial, Intact Financial 
-- 
-- Thu May 08, 2014 04:24AM EDT
-- None



May 8 (Reuters) - Securities analysts revised their ratings and price targets on several Canadian companies, including Avigilon Corp, CI Financial and Intact Financial, on Thursday.

HIGHLIGHTS * Avigilon Corp <AVO.TO>: Raymond James reinstates with outperform rating  * CI Financial <CIX.TO>: Canaccord Genuity, National Bank Financial raise target price on co * Intact Financial <IFC.TO>: National Bank Financial cuts to sector perform from outperform  Following is a summary of research actions on Canadian companies reported by Reuters on Thursday. Stock entries are in alphabetical order.  * Altus Group <AIF.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$23; rating buy  * Avigilon Corp <AVO.TO>: Raymond James reinstates with outperform rating  * Canyon Services Group <FRC.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$20; rating buy * Churchill Corp <CUQ.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$14.50 from C$11.75 * CI Financial <CIX.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$41.25 from C$40; buy * CI Financial <CIX.TO>: National Bank Financial raises target price to C$43 from C$42 * Encana Corporation <ECA.N>: National Bank Financial ups to outperform from sector perform * Encana Corporation <ECA.N>: National Bank Financial raises target to $28 from $25.50  * Intact Financial <IFC.TO>: National Bank Financial cuts to sector perform from outperform * Intact Financial <IFC.TO>: National Bank Financial ups target to C$75 from C$74  * Killam Properties <KMP.TO>: Canaccord Genuity cuts target price to C$11; rating hold * Midway Gold <MDW.TO>: Canaccord Genuity cuts target price to C$1.30; speculative buy  * Paramount Resources <POU.TO>: Canaccord Genuity raises target price to C$70; rating buy * Tim Hortons <THI.TO>: Canaccord Genuity cuts target price to C$58 from C$59; rating hold * Trican Well Service <TCW.TO>: National Bank Financial raises target to C$16 from C$15 * Trinidad Drilling <TDG.TO>: National Bank Financial raises target to C$14.50 from C$13